>\n<a href=\"http://fgosimulator.webcrow.jp/Material/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffgosimulator.webcrow.jp%2FMaterial%2F&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=6092e4cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://fgosimulator.webcrow.jp/Material/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>-戒賭熱線-</strong> <br />\nTEL: 183 4633 <br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkjc.com/responsible-gambling/images/footer_icon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fresponsible-gambling%2Fimages%2Ffooter_icon.jpg&h=f8bd194a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n資助被新選組壓榨到時薪得20文(1串永樂錢)嘅小Nobu<br />\n<strong>-Post Template-</strong> <br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/LlMBdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FLlMBdf&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=01c3146d\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/LlMBdf</a> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>-高登FGO區黑名單-</strong> <br />\n1.長期良美 <br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/20lTYan.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F20lTYan.jpg&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=d8ee5074\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/20lTYan.jpg</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/0Jpj3XR.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0Jpj3XR.jpg&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8a0cb53e\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/0Jpj3XR.jpg</a> <br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/ogNh2TM.png?1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FogNh2TM.png%3F1&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=144ccd04\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/ogNh2TM.png?1</a> <br />\n0課<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廿</span></span>*****以上 <br />\n歐盟會長、法老王 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>慎入慎盲</strong></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n2.字智波帶土 <br />\n(開台1符中限定) <br />\n<br />\n3.西田望見 <br />\n梅林pickup， <br />\n多次曬出梅林， <br />\n但聲明自己只係想抽積子， <br />\n直接貼圖傷害一眾梅林難民弱小心靈。 <br />\n<br />\n4.平凡痴線佬 <br />\n個個都準備8號 ALL IN CSOR <br />\n我好期待睇大家抽 <br />\n祝人人8號中CSOR <br />\n利申 我果隻CSOR 陪左我成年了 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 5.某教主 <br />\n2符中金閃 776石寶3希望的影像:</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t0Z3vO4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft0Z3vO4.jpg&h=3d3b9e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">BBちゃんの逆襲</span></strong><br />\n</span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eZ7m196.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZ7m196.png&h=ae78cd14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JfHNn9K2WEE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJfHNn9K2WEE&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZohOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=8f4ce207\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JfHNn9K2WEE</a>"},{"pid":"650d2d2eb46bf517b6f84a53d5769b55f4d9ae67","tid":221163,"uid":85045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:32:03.000Z","msg":"係街copy唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625b4d0a41e473283efb1015bb239911c40a1980","tid":221163,"uid":12471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"Sorry 負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d370c8fe3b34929eb138ea9bbd8c7f0195117c80","tid":221163,"uid":76364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係街copy唔晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辛苦哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"482c9fd49aa34c9af1061c22b6f08f1d